    "nacreii_flag = False.To perform a Monte Carlo analysis of the SM predictions taking into account uncertainties (similar to the one presented in Ref.",
    "[35]):The output maps out the probability distributions, shown in Fig. 3, where the light elements at the end of the BBN era are predicted within the SM via a MC analysis that involves: (i) a cosmological prior on the cosmic baryon abundance; (ii) a particle-physics measurement prior on the neutron lifetime; and (iii) a dedicated treatment of the uncertainties in the rates of the nuclear processes.",
